  "description": "OSPREY, OSTERIA, and OCEANIC — the shore family. Azulejo blue, porto wine, phosphorescent teal. The ShoreSystem blessing (B012) connects OSPREY and OSTERIA through 5 coastline cultural datasets; OCEANIC provides the intertidal zone where land-breath meets water. The tide in balance — coastal instruments sharing the ShoreSystem data, OCEANIC connecting them to open water.",
